UEFA Champions League ITV Highlights 2016-03-09 HDTV 1080p 2ch x265 [S-Less]

Action from the opening set of last-16 second-leg ties, including Chelsea v Paris Saint-Germain at Stamford Bridge, and Zenit St Petersburg v Benfica at Petrovsky Stadium. Plus, a look back at last night's fixtures, as Real Madrid hosted AS Roma at the Bernabeu, and VfL Wolfsburg welcomed Gent to Volkswagen Arena. Mark Pougatch presents, with analysis from Roy Keane and Lee Dixon, and commentary by Clive Tyldesley and Sam Matterface
